      <hedline>
        <hl1>Evolution, an Endangered Subject</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Mary McLemore letter on Feb 1 article about evolution asserts that evolution is theory not fact</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>The author does a fine job of dancing around the truth that evolution is a theory, not a fact, though it's on firmer ground than global warming. Oh, wait, they couldn't find any evidence of that, so it's climate change now, isn't it?</p>
        <p>MARY MCLEMORE  Autaugaville, Ala.</p>
      </block>
